name: MediPharm Labs Corp.
longDescription: MediPharm Labs Corp, along with its subsidiaries, produces purified, pharmaceutical-like cannabis extracts and related derivative products. The company generates revenue from Private label, White label, the Tolling process, and others. Some of its vape brands are Northern Lights, Blue Dream Pink Kush and GG4. Its geographical segments are Canada and Australia.
